channel.title: Anyone help me? (Fixed) TrisidiaX - New Problem!
channel.description:
[b]Hey Guys now i have a new problem when going inside my client and clicking run it opens a tab webclient/popout client - i clicked popout client and it opens and closes really fast??? [/b] :palm: :palm:
[center][img]http://i1361.photobucket.com/albums/r679/haviland66/error_zps9cafd950.png[/img]
[b]Should be really easy for someone that knows what there doing unlike me :( Anyone know where i have to go to fix this problem?
Problem was inside the cache they have removed the map folder with the content inside. if anyone needs the fixed cache feel free to message me.
Thanks Josh[/b][/center]

you’re missing the mapConfig file.

Delete the cache and try again.
